{"tid":2034088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Twitter要人] 邊睇三上悠亞邊勾結外國勢力！","createTime":"2020-05-25T04:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T05:22:35.000Z","uid":78020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f698b4783a9f779f4921fa3aabc07bb18d98f42c","tid":2034088,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"TLDR: 與其做任務，不如正常咁用<br />\n<br />\n小弟見到連登上嘅Twitter post都係以做任為主，但其實做任務BOT對大部分人嚟講係好難持之以恆。<br />\n<br />\n無錯，任務bot係好易做，但重複作業加上feel唔到實際效果，係好難要大部分人長keep嘅<br />\n<br />\n所以，我建議大家正常用Twitter，唔想自己摸索嘅可以參考以下步驟<br />\n<br />\n1) 開ac，名同id<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">儘量唔好</span></strong>係咩HKers、standwithhk01之類，可以個人化啲<br />\n<br />\n2) 揀相，個人認為<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好特登揀文宣、手足相</strong></span>，可以揀同你興趣有關嘅，高達又好ironman又好猫狗都好，吸引左普通外國人follow 你先<br />\n<br />\n3) Twitter 會問你對咩有興趣，除左揀香港、standwithhongkong之類，記住揀同你興趣有關嘅，一個100%香港新聞嘅Twitter 唔會令你keep住想上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bj5A1dW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbj5A1dW.jpg&h=4eb0076e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁佢會即刻推介你follow 一啲人，可能佢估我係男人，就推介左三上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVqmckZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVqmckZ.jpg&h=1211b691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4) 開左ac啦，首先去search下你個人興趣嘅關鍵字。我當你鐘意marvel啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KrApUzG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrApUzG.jpg&h=cd9bd7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nfollow左啲官方(剔號) users，Twitter 會比好多users 建議你follow，即管follow哂，跟手搵下啲有相同興趣嘅人follow <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqP2Ge8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqP2Ge8.jpg&h=fd9fb8ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又會比好多建議你，follow 一個又彈一個，永續follow<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0TA5D12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0TA5D12.jpg&h=ac539601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好怕，隨便鳩follow，Twitter 好多人會隨便follow back 嘅，咁你就會有第一班普通用户followers <br />\n<br />\n5) 多啲出post，share下啲非政治內容，多啲rt &amp; like人地嘅post，交流下，keep 住Twitter 有你真心鐘意睇嘅內容，咁會輕鬆啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0a9mgt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0a9mgt.jpg&h=f2093451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6) 想有多啲手足follow，可以用下手足互科，followbackhongkong呢類tag，follow 多左亦會自然見到啲「每日任務」自己彈過嚟<br />\n<br />\n7) 做文宣時用嘅tag，除左用standwithhongkong、光復香港時代革命呢啲同溫層tag，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">更應該用 香港、hongkong，五毛會主力攻佔呢啲一般tag</span></strong>。甚至可以騎劫對家嘅tag，如ACAC、acacsince5859、missyoutoo，不過清楚個前因後果先會玩得好啲<br />\n<br />\n8) 多啲用自己語言解釋香港呢幾10年嘅問題，深入啲解釋比外國人聽<br />\n<br />\n9) 唔好驚圍爐，唔好歧視圍爐，亦唔好對啲爐太上心，畢竟有人就有衝突。但長遠建立一個香港人Twitter 社群係好緊要嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n10) 保持警覺，唔好隨便同人講自己去左邊，做過咩，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好自爆，</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有人試過懷疑比狗套料</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n11) 仲有一樣嘢，唔好咁快對人哋嘅政治事件代表香港人去 HKers stand with you心心，除非係針對支共嘅國際事件。你識嗰種語言，做足功課，我覺得完全可以有立場同參與討論，但唔洗代表香港。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">唔好隨便吹雞當係任務</span></span>。之前日本檢察官退休年齡修例就試過一次小炒，不過好彩無咩大後果。<br />\n<br />\n12) 重要設定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jU0FB9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjU0FB9P.jpg&h=78ded272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/raoPvuQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FraoPvuQ.jpg&h=774d6eab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3b21f149a91e8e8ef00c17acec2c931636fbe61","tid":2034088,"uid":78020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f09d59fa4ff3044f0252d179928604689bf4fbd4","tid":2034088,"uid":